2.x.x
------------------
NEW FEATURES:
- Added "invoice" type tag. (Alex Pgnoni)
- VAT description fields (Alex Pagnoni)
- Added row counter. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Added method for getting last invoice date. (Alex Pagnoni)

CHANGES:
- Updated minimum Innowork Core version to 3.3.0. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Updated code with namespaces. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Quantity is now decimal. (Alex Pagnoni)



2.0.0 - 2014/01/11
------------------
CHANGES:
- Refactoring for Innomatic. (Alex Pagnoni)



1.3.1 - 2004/10/15
------------------
NEW FEATURES:
- Added firstname and lastname tags to invoice template. (Alex Pagnoni)



1.3 - 2004/07/15
----------------
CHANGES:
- Now invoice rows amount is no more formatted when editing an invoice. (Alex Pagnoni)



1.2 - 2004/04/15
----------------
NEW FEATURES:
- Added month filter. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Added support for second fiscal code in invoice template. (Alex Pagnoni)

CHANGES:
- Now changes are logged. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Now InnoworkDirectory 1.2 is required. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Only companies of type customer or customer/supplier are listed. (Alex Pagnoni)

FIXES:
- The item cache now gets flushed when updating the paidamount field through
  InnoworkInvoice->SetPaidAmount(). (Alex Pagnoni)
- Fixed missing dispatcher descriptor in invoice payment panel. (Alex Pagnoni)



