- Added quantity and discount fields in invoice rows. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Improved speed. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Added "number" to the searchable keys. (Alex Pagnoni)

CHANGES:
- Adapted to Innowork Core 2.1 organization. (Alex Pagnoni)

FIXES:
- Fixed item type definition in xenbilling.library. (Alex Pagnoni)
- Fixed "Edit payment" button in payments preferences. (Alex Pagnoni)



